{"tid":1425540,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"要求政府加強對「已知危險狗隻」管制","createTime":"2019-08-06T18:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:39:48.000Z","uid":253240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"10d5eee9d38af501b2cae8cd47ce2c099cf98c2e","tid":1425540,"uid":253240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:36:31.000Z","msg":"現時被列入「格鬥狗隻」類別的品種包括比特鬥牛㹴、日本土佐犬、巴西非拉狗及阿根廷杜告狗，現時分類為「已知危險狗隻」的狗隻，必須在90內由註冊獸醫進行絕育手術，否則主人便違法。 <br />\n<br />\n可唔可以要求加入埋警務人員？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0Gn6GG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0Gn6GG.png&h=e15a2172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本土佐犬(左上圖)、比特鬥牛㹴(右上圖)、阿根廷杜告狗(左下圖)、巴西非拉狗(右下圖)被列入「格鬥狗隻」類別。(資料圖片)"},{"pid":"ec138f54bb21535be0a2f9e72588cdbd68ee5728","tid":1425540,"uid":253240,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n6KEpuw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn6KEpuw.png&h=c4ff6945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第五類"}]}